RULE: FILE_FIRST_APPROACH
Before creating any new file:
1. SEARCH: Always search the codebase for similar existing files
2. EXAMINE: Thoroughly examine file purpose and content before modification
3. EXTEND: Prefer extending existing files over creating new ones
4. CONSOLIDATE: Identify opportunities to merge similar functionality
5. VALIDATE: Confirm file dependencies and references before changes
6. DOCUMENT: Clearly explain why a new file is necessary if created
7. CLEAN: Remove any temporary or redundant files after completing tasks